<h2>Conservatory Delays and Cancellations March 11</h2>
<p class="publisheddate">Fri, March 11, 2016</p>	

<p>
	Due to winter weather conditions, the School of Music opening is delayed today, March 11, until 12 noon. &nbsp;All Kindermusik classes are cancelled. School of Dance classes are cancelled, but Teachers&#39; Dance Exams and the School of Dance special evening event will proceed.</p>


<!--<a href="http://maritimeconservatory.com/News/bulletin/conservatory-openings-delayed-March-11" title="Conservatory Delays and Cancellations March 11">Read entire article »</a>-->
